WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.660
In direct exchange for driving their infrastructure consumption, Amazon Web

00:00:04.660 --> 00:00:09.320
Services provides AppsFlyer with unprecedented, highly structured sales acceleration. This

00:00:09.320 --> 00:00:13.980
powerful dynamic elevates our relationship into a deeply strategic global

00:00:13.980 --> 00:00:18.640
alliance, built firmly on three foundational pillars which include direct

00:00:18.640 --> 00:00:23.300
financial investments into joint initiatives, a highly orchestrated co-sell motion,

00:00:23.300 --> 00:00:27.960
and seamless, lucrative access to their integrated marketplace.
